    "perHand is a LABEL ONLY. It never enters a calculation. Volume for one set is",
    "always weightKg * reps — never doubled for a pair of dumbbells. A 20 kg curl",
    "for 10 reps is 200, exactly as entered.",
    "",
    "Bodyweight movements still store weightKg: it means ADDED weight, and defaults to 0.",
    "A set of 0 kg x 12 reps is valid and contributes 0 to volume.",
    "",
    "Every exercise seeded here must have custom: false, so the user can tell the",
    "preloaded library apart from their own additions and a future seed update can",
    "safely replace the non-custom rows."
